  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "When we came to the group, they teach us, they teach us maybe that was the city, near the city that's in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They send us, they teach us how to fight, if you come to the German, how to fight with a knife, how to [? find, ?] how to fight, things like this.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it's very complicated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You cannot say what I don't want to do, to do this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And you was doing with understanding, and you know what can happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "When we came, a lot of people, they saved us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But every time when a group goes, the groups, they send six persons, seven persons, and they [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Or they doesn't come back at all, or it's come back a few.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The first time after [? this ?] what I [? told us ?] they give us the uniform of the army.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the first time when after that, was they teach us how to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Everything, it was short.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "For [INAUDIBLE], they teach us, and they tell [? know ?] what we [? will. ?] Officers didn't give us some uniforms.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "No, because we go to there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "You cannot have some papers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We leave all the papers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "What you have, you cannot take with you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The first time, it was good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We brought, we brought one, one German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And what they was doing, that was not our business.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We bring them, and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And the second, the second time, that was 1944, maybe June or July, I was wounded.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I went to, to make what that's the job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we was seven or eight people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I was wounded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And they take us, they take me from [? off, ?] from the, from the place where there became near to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
